en-US.title: Planned Parenthood - St. Albans Health Center
en-US.description: This health center, previously located at 80 Fairfield St, St Albans City, VT 05478, served as an inclusive and LGBTQ+ friendly medical center, offering informed-consent clinic services suitable for the transgender community. However, it is now permanently closed.
